This paper deals with constraint solving and rule-based reasoning, which are topics commonly associated with artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the methodology for extending a software platform, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a Simple Fluent Calculus (SFC), which is a logical framework and falls under logic in computer science (cs.LO). Finally, the paper discusses the generation of explanatory traces, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR).
